      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for daily transportation. The engine and transmission are fully operational, though you should expect the typical mechanical sounds and minor fluid seepage associated with a car of this age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery. It has been recently serviced for basic maintenance, making it a solid choice for someone seeking a functional car at a reasonable price point.",
