      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is a solid, honest performer that has served its previous owners well! While it shows some expected signs of use and character consistent with its age, it remains a reliable driver that's ready for its next chapter. It's the perfect opportunity to get into a quality model at a very accessible price point\u2014come see the value for yourself!",
