      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. It's been well-loved and is just waiting for its next adventure. Come by and take it for a spin, I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love how it drives!",
      "price": 28900.0,
