    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive double-VANOS service and a rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common E46 chassis weak points. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and lateral grip expected of the M-division. While the exterior shows minor patina from spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are exceptionally sharp.",
      "price": 31500.0,
