    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 luxury sport sedan that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily usability. The deep obsidian black exterior retains a high-gloss finish, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear bumper. Inside, the charcoal leather interior is in excellent shape, with minimal creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster and a smoke-free environment. All electronics, including the panoramic sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and premium 12-speaker audio system, function perfectly. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust; it comes with a complete service history, including a recent synthetic oil change and a fresh set of brake pads. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. It shifts smoothly through all gears and provides a quiet, composed ride. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle for someone looking for a premium experience without the new-car price tag. Clean title in hand and ready for its next owner.",
